| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3611 — Recovery Inhibition (blackbasta)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c0fc6dd2-94eb-5210-b181-f621d0c701e9"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
